data.description: RING YOUR BUYERS!!!! THIS IS A LARGE HOME LOCATED IN THE HIGHLY DESIRABLE COMMUNITY OF VIZCAYA AT THE HAMMOCKS. NEW ROOF REPLACED IN 2017, A/C UNIT REPLACED IN 2016, ACCORDION SHUTTERS LOCATED ON THE SECOND FLOOR WINDOWS, PANELS FOR THE GROUND FLOOR WINDOWS/DOORS, REMODELED PATIO AREA. BEAUTIFUL PORCELAIN FLOORING THROUGHOUT THE GROUND FLOOR LEVEL, UPDATED KITCHEN WITH STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, AND BONUS ROOM WHICH COULD BE CLOSED OFF AND MADE INTO A 5TH BEDROOM. OAK WOOD STAIRCASE, WOOD LAMINATE FLOORING THROUGHOUT THE SECOND FLOOR, LARGE MASTER BEDROOM WITH OFFICE NOOK, EXTRA LARGE WALK IN CLOSET. COMMUNITY POOL CLOSE TO THE HOUSE. OWNERS HAVE ACCESS TO "WILD LIME PARK" EQUIPPED WITH SOCCER FIELDS, LAKES, KIDS PLAY GROUND, EXERCISE AREA, AND COMMUNITY SHELTER FOR BIRTHDAYS AND EVENTS!
